headline: M&T Bank Corporation to Participate in the Barclays Global Financial Services Conference
summary: M&T Bank Corporation ("M&T") (NYSE:MTB) will participate in the Barclays Global Financial Services Conference being held in New York City. Representatives of M&T are scheduled to deliver a presentation to investors and analysts on September 10, 2025, at 9:45 am (ET).
